import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormBuilder, FormGroup } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ standalone: true, selector: 'app-login', templateUrl: './login.component.html', styleUrls: ['./login.component.css'] }) export default class LoginComponent implements OnInit { loginForm: FormGroup; constructor( private fb: FormBuilder ){ } ngOnInit(): void { } createLoginForm(){ this.loginForm = this.fb } }
